OPTIMIZE: 
all require functions turned into error statments
since when a transaction reverts, 
it consumes far less gas compared to require statments
when there is multiple boolean checks, 
De Morgan Theorem is used
~(A AND B) <==> (~A OR ~B) 
~(A OR B) <==> (~A AND ~B)
